  "text": "In sections 3 and 4, we have discussed parameters such as C L , C R , C that affect the renormalization scheme in a relatively trivial way. They change only the explicit form of O R and O L but do not change the corresponding SFT solution. In contrast, parameters C 1 , C 0 and C [CITATION_1] 0 appear at first glance to affect the renormalization scheme and the SFT solution. Let's examine these in some detail.",
